{"tid":336093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一地兩檢不違基本法　涂謹申：可撥部西九站份土地予內地","createTime":"2017-07-26T06:40:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-26T07:08:03.000Z","uid":49388,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0851179c020bf480b4dcd08d5a1f5cd6cf9de492","tid":336093,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:40:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/港聞/76421/實施一地兩檢不違基本法-涂謹申-港可撥部西九站份土地予內地\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2F76421%2F%E5%AF%A6%E6%96%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%B0%E5%85%A9%E6%AA%A2%E4%B8%8D%E9%81%95%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%B3%95-%E6%B6%82%E8%AC%B9%E7%94%B3-%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%AF%E6%92%A5%E9%83%A8%E8%A5%BF%E4%B9%9D%E7%AB%99%E4%BB%BD%E5%9C%9F%E5%9C%B0%E4%BA%88%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0&d=R39rRjhGqRHJV8Ki76lo2mi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=59eaa940\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/港聞/76421/實施一地兩檢不違基本法-涂謹申-港可撥部西九站份土地予內地</a><br />\n<br />\n廣深港高鐵預計明年中落成，惟西九總站實施一地兩檢問題仍未有定案。立法會議員涂謹申認為可撥歸部份土地予內地政府，以免出現內地人員在港執法情況，惟現屆政府無法給予市民信心，始令執行上有困難。<br />\n涂謹申今早接受電台訪問時指，在西九站內實施一地兩檢，法律及技術上均可行，香港可將該處幾千呎土地撥歸內地政府，等於縮少香港領土範圍，此做法可避免抵觸《基本法》有關內地人員不能在港執法的條文。惟涂謹申表示「主要係信心問題」，因現屆政府無法給予市民信心可有效執行一地兩檢，市民亦會擔心開此先例後，香港會否「一路縮細」，但長遠而言，涂認為可落實一地兩檢。"},{"pid":"5ee947f24144ad12b751b9a2344cfc4e893de11e","tid":336093,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:42:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba2d6aa47da26e874678e68b83af17225e7550ff","tid":336093,"uid":12565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:51:02.000Z","msg":"輕鬆賣港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n民主黨ho ball <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d007777922ad91cce590b6891cc1ab3454036e74","tid":336093,"uid":104793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:55:35.000Z","msg":"屌咁都講得出，仲衰過建制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b87a9c0c3b73295f17584e8b8025848fc361591","tid":336093,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T07:06:44.000Z","msg":"撥地是中國自古以來習慣<br />\n<br />\n中國將外蒙古與海參威撥交外國管理合情合法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"352e2f54e000e01e2ddf322bcc6029b42f8393d5","tid":336093,"uid":106929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T07:08:03.000Z","msg":"民主黨又贏"}]}